{
  "stem": "1975.2",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But we were not-- we were aware sometimes after-- after the turning between-- after the 1941, we we knew that-- because some soldiers, and some Jewish soldiers who were able to escape and who came to certain-- Lithuanian army-- came-- and especially one that was stationed in-- in-- in our city said that everybody in the city was taken out and killed.",
      "word_count": 62
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They were taken out to a secluded place, about three kilometers.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And, first of all, they separated the men.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then they had the men in a seclusion, and then the women, children, and elderly people separately.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So first of all, in-- in August, they claim sometimes in the middle of August, they took out the men, and they took them to [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was a little forest, a young forest.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they dug there-- they made them dig their graves, and they would-- they shot them.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then a couple days later, like, seven, eight days later, they took the children, the women, and the-- and the elderly people.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they-- they were also shot, and they had the same fate the men.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We-- every time they came with the new-- new ideas-- like there was, later, the children actually, were by-- there were still some children who were hiding.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they-- they came in when the men and women were out to work.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They came in and they surrounded the ghetto, came in with-- with autobuses, which were the-- the windows were tinted-- and-- that you cannot look inside.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they came out, and they took-- they gave the order to the police.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We had a Jewish police in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
